    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet149"/>, quoted according to
                    the catalogue description in <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><citedRange unit="page">584</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab> 
                        ተአምሪሁ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ትንብልናሁ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወሶበ፡ ተፈጸመት፡ አሐቲ፡ ዓመት፡ ሐለፈ፡ እድሜሁ፡ ለአብራድዮስ፡
                        ወአልቦ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ዘወሀቦ፡ ለዝኩ፡ ባዕል፡ እምንዋዩ፡ እስመ፡ ሰይጣን፡ <sic>አወሮ፡</sic> አእይንቲሁ፡
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab>
                        ወዝኩሰ፡ አብራድዮስ፡ ረሰየ፡ ንብረቶ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያኑ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ወነበረ፡ እንዘ፡ ይትለአክ፡ እስከ፡ ዕለተ፡ ፍልሰቱ፡
                        ወኢተመይጠ፡ ይግበር፡ ምግባረ፡ አመፃ። ዳግመ፡ ወኢዕከየ፡ ጸሎቱ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
